    <div class="body">
        <p>In configuration file, we need tu use only the key <em>data</em> for the translate resource. I whish unified Zend_Application_Resource_Translate with the improvement of Zend_Translate (ndlr args of constructor become an array). Before this update, the name of the second argument was actually <em>$data</em>. But, now translations source data use the key <em>content</em>.</p>

<p>I think it would depreciate the use of <em>data</em>.</p>

